### Layout Structure

```tsx
// Root layout structure
<div className="min-h-screen bg-whatsapp-beige flex">
  <Sidebar /> {/* w-64 fixed sidebar */}
  <main className="flex-1 overflow-auto bg-white">
    <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-8">
      {children}
    </div>
  </main>
</div>
```

**Page Layout Pattern:**
```tsx
<div className="space-y-8">
  {/* Page header */}
  <header className="flex items-center justify-between">
    <h1 className="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-whatsapp-dark-teal">
      Page Title
    </h1>
    <p className="text-sm text-gray-600">Subtitle or description</p>
  </header>

  {/* Content sections */}
  <section className="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
    {/* Cards */}
  </section>
</div>
```

