### Icons (lucide-react)

Always use `lucide-react` for icons. Standard size is 20.

```tsx
import { LayoutDashboard, Users, FileText, Calendar, Settings } from 'lucide-react';

<Icon size={20} />
```

**Common icons:**
- `LayoutDashboard` - Dashboard
- `Users` - Entities/Cases
- `FileText` - Templates
- `Calendar` - Calendar view
- `Settings` - Settings
- `Plus` - Add/Create
- `Edit` - Edit
- `Trash2` - Delete
- `Image` - Images
- `Video` - Videos
- `Link` - Links
- `Clock` - Time/Schedule
- `AlertCircle` - Warnings
- `CheckCircle` - Success

